BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Ce2Hy85rxKmmgE9KWN-Od
SUMMARY:Goose Ridge: Library Sale & Tasting
DTSTAMP:20260307T235608Z
DTSTART:20260308T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our Library Sale & Tasting\, beginning February 27t
	h and available for a limited time while supplies last. \n\nWe’re opening 
	the cellar and bringing back select library wines for a special tasting an
	d sale at Goose Ridge Woodinville. \n\nEnjoy the opportunity to purchase b
	eautifully aged wines from past vintages. Whether you’re looking to restoc
	k a favorite vintage or discover a hidden gem from our cellar\, this is th
	e perfect time to explore our library collection. Inventory is limited. Av
	ailable while supplies last.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/deta
