	Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater for the Winter Student Showcase! \n
	\nWatch as our talented students—ranging from beginner to advanced levels—
	take the stage to craft spontaneous\, engaging\, and often hilarious impro
	v scenes right before your eyes. Our 300\, 400\, and 500-level students wi
	ll showcase their newly honed skills\, giving you an exclusive preview of 
	the next generation of improv stars. \n\nYou’ll experience a variety of pe
	rformance styles inspired by UP’s mainstage shows\, making for an unpredic
	table and highly entertaining night. Stick around after the show to meet t
	he performers—you’ll be able to say\, “I saw them before they were famous!
	” \n\n6:00pm: Chad Sunday 300\, Bestock 400\, Tim 400\, Tony 500\n\n8:00pm
