BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:t8zena46WLHMlf2BWgmFZ
SUMMARY:Clock-Out Lounge Presents: Spike Einbinder & Honey Pluton comedy to
	ur with guest Dewa Dorje
DTSTAMP:20260307T235608Z
DTSTART:20260310T203000Z
DESCRIPTION:Clock-Out Lounge Presents:Spike Einbinder & Honey Plutonwith sp
	ecial guest Dewa Dorje Tuesday\\\, March 10th\\\, 8:00 PM doors21+$20adv/$
	25 dos Spike Einbinder and Honey Pluton hit the West Coast from NYC to spl
	it an hour of stand-up comedy! Expect transsexual musing\\\, tales of lore
	\\\, and hilarity ensuing. Honey Pluton is a stand-up comedian and theatri
	cal performer with 10 years of experience spanning stage\\\, film\\\, and 
	screen. Hes creatively inspired by disruption\\\, risk-taking\\\, and the 
	liminal thresholds that blur states of consciousness. He is nationally tou
	ring his solo show Ive Always Been Like This to sold-out crowds across the
	 country and is also the host of the weekly podcast Up Good with Honey Plu
	ton. Spike Einbinder is a comedian\\\, actor\\\, writer\\\, drag performer
	\\\, and 6\\\,000-year-old shapeshifting demon from Los Angeles. His work 
	combines body horror\\\, surrealism\\\, and dark comedy. He has featured r
	oles in HBOs Los Espookys\\\, as well as A24s You Hurt My Feelings and Pro
	blemista. He has performed his live solo comedy hours Visions and Im Not S
	cared m Not Insane to sold-out crowds.\n\nhttps://clockoutlounge.com/event
	/clock-out-lounge-presents-spike-einbinder-honey-pluton/\n\nFrom Clock-Out
	 Lounge
URL:https://clockoutlounge.com/event/clock-out-lounge-presents-spike-einbin
	der-honey-pluton/
LOCATION:Clock-Out Lounge\\\, 4864 Beacon Ave S\\\, Seattle\\\, 98108\\\, U
	nited States Of America
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:clock-out-lounge
CATEGORIES:Clock-Out Lounge
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
